// OpenClaw Configuration Template
// 复制为 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 并填入你的 API keys
// 文档: https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/configuration
{
  // === 环境变量 ===
  "env": {
    "vars": {
      // LLM Provider (至少填一个)
      // "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "__YOUR_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY__",
      // "OPENAI_API_KEY": "__YOUR_OPENAI_API_KEY__",
      // "GOOGLE_API_KEY": "__YOUR_GOOGLE_API_KEY__",

      // Chat Channel (至少填一个)
      // "DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN": "__YOUR_DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN__",
      // 飞书在 channels.feishu 中配置

      // 可选
      // "GITHUB_TOKEN": "__YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN__"
    }
  },

  // === Gateway ===
  "gateway": {
    "port": 3456,
    "mode": "production"
  },

  // === Agent 默认配置 ===
  "agents": {
    "defaults": {
      "model": {
        "primary": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6"
      }
    }
  },

  // === 模型配置 ===
  "models": {
    "providers": {
      // Anthropic API Key 模式
      // "anthropic": { "api": "anthropic" },

      // 或 setup-token 模式（无需 API key）
      // 用 openclaw models auth setup-token --provider anthropic 配置
    }
  },

  // === 记忆系统 ===
  "memory": {
    "backend": "qmd",
    "citations": "auto",
    "qmd": {
      "command": "__HOME__/.openclaw/scripts/qmd-safe.sh",
      "searchMode": "search",
      "includeDefaultMemory": true,
      "update": {
        "interval": "5m",
        "debounceMs": 15000,
        "onBoot": true
      },
      "limits": {
        "maxResults": 10,
        "timeoutMs": 60000
      }
    }
  },

  // === Chat Channels ===
  "channels": {
    // Discord
    // "discord": {
    //   "allowlist": [{
    //     "guild": "__YOUR_DISCORD_GUILD_ID__",
    //     "users": ["__YOUR_DISCORD_USER_ID__"]
    //   }]
    // },

    // 飞书
    // "feishu": {
    //   "appId": "__YOUR_FEISHU_APP_ID__",
    //   "appSecret": "__YOUR_FEISHU_APP_SECRET__"
    // }
  },

  // === ACP (Coding Agents) ===
  "acp": {
    "enabled": true,
    "dispatch": { "enabled": true },
    "backend": "acpx",
    "defaultAgent": "codex",
    "allowedAgents": ["pi", "claude", "codex", "opencode", "gemini"],
    "maxConcurrentSessions": 4
  },

  // === 工具配置 ===
  "tools": {
    "profile": "full"
  },

  // === Skills ===
  "skills": {
    "load": { "watch": false },
    "install": { "nodeManager": "npm" }
  },

  // === Cron ===
  "cron": {
    "maxConcurrentRuns": 3
  },

  // === 日志 ===
  "logging": {
    "level": "info",
    "file": true,
    "consoleLevel": "warn"
  },

  // === Session ===
  "session": {
    "dmScope": "user"
  },

  // === 浏览器 ===
  "browser": {
    "enabled": true,
    "headless": true
  },

  // === Workspace ===
  // setup.sh 会自动设置
  // "workspace": "__HOME__/clawd"
}
